commit.message:
Miscellaneous fixes for Celer Web SDK integration

- Fix the oracle ABI string
- Supply the condition deadline properly with current block number + 10
- Add a 1s delay between user and provider conditional payments
- Remove celer-sdk and use the NPM package instead
- Properly stop HDWalletProvider in generate-keys.js
- Update celer_client binaries
- Update README
